reviewText: Had to watch on my computer, but good fun!

Material like this has a tendency to disappear from view.

This is a VHS recording of a live talk Vladimir was giving. Dont expect a really picture or 5.1 surround sound. I enjoyed it, but I enjoy watching lecture on VHS anyway.
This is set in the 1970s, so the newsgathering technique is not up with our times, but laying that aside it is not bad. The ending comes as an almost complete surprise.
